title: Good but WAY TOO MANY ADS!!
text: Look, I absolutely love Spotify. Good music, podcasts, etc. but I cannot explain how annoying your ads are! I would understand if they played every now and then, but it after every song (I can’t make this up). And not tryna be mean, but I don’t plan on paying just to nat hear ads and choose songs. If this ad thing don’t stop, I’m probably gonna go back to Amazon Music.
